subsections.text_content:
Clause 4.2.2.2 and clause 4.2.2.3 are applied with the differences that the NF service consumers (e.g. PCF) shall include (if available) in SpendingLimitContext data structure:
-	the IMSI of the user within the "supi" attribute;
-	the MSISDN of the user within the "gpsi" attribute;
